Before we begin let us review the Splinter bids. You bid splinter if:
 
- Partner opens 1@H/1@S
- You have 4-card support
- You have a singleton (it could be an honor) or void. 
- You have 13-16 dummy points. Remember, with 17+ dummy points you bid Jacoby 2N even if you have a singleton.
- You can bid splinter if the singleton is an Ace.|
